Package: washr
Type: Package
Title: Design, Implementation and Analysis of Urban Water and Sanitation Surveys
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Ernest Guevarra <ernestgmd@gmail.com> [aut, cre]", 
    "Valid International <office@validinternational.org> [cph]"
  ))
Description: Provides the necessary functions that support the design,
    implementation and analysis of Water and Sanitation for the Urban Poor
    (WSUP) Urban Water and Sanitation Survey. It also includes functions that
    implement a Shiny application for visulasing and mapping results of the
    survey.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
